<td valign="top"><span class="label">Figure 5 
				</span><span class="capture-id">
                  <p><b>Common European consensus block regions</b>. Overlapping consensus block regions from each consensus block defined from MDBlocks (MD), HapBlock (HB), and Gabriel's method
                     (GA). Consensus blocks shown from each method are defined at a threshold of 80% using all SNPs with at least a 10% MAF. The SNP positions are shown in the last track.</p>

               </span><br /></td>
</tr>
